OL,3,CMan charged over murder of woman
OL,4,Cwalking to meet mum for coffee
OL,6,FA man has been charged with the murder
OL,7,Fof a 51-year-old woman from Greater
OL,8,FManchester who was stabbed to death
OL,9,Fwhile walking to meet her mother.
OL,11,FMichelle Hodgkinson was attacked on
OL,12,FEdge Lane in Droylsden on Friday 2
OL,13,FJune, 2023, and died at the scene.
OL,15,FIn a statement in the immediate
OL,16,Faftermath of her death, Michelle's
OL,17,Ffamily described her as their 'rock'
OL,18,Fand 'biggest cheerleader.'
OL,20,F(GMP) said it had now charged 29-year-
OL,21,Fold Paul Hughes with murder.
