OL,6,FHe has been remanded in a secure
OL,7,Fmental health hospital, where he
OL,8,Fremains under treatment. He will next
OL,9,Fappear at andMagistrates court on
OL,10,FThursday 6 June 2024.
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Danny Lee of GMP's
OL,13,FMajor Incident Team said: "We
OL,14,Funderstand this tragedy may have
OL,15,Fincreased the community concerns in
OL,16,Frelation to knife crime, but we would
OL,17,Flike to stress this is a very rare
OL,18,Ftype of incident.
